yself).  After a quick thankyou, our erstwhile savior checked on Calare, saw she was fine, and dissappeared into the ether.<br><br>If for nothing else, that made FV worth it for me. <p>Denoi Fishwhiskers<BR>Taruun of Shar Val<BR><BR>Master Cook <BR>Lousy Fletcher<BR>Grandmaster Lech<BR><I>"I can picture in my mind a world without war, a world without hate. And I can picture us attacking that world, because they'd never expect it." -- Jack Handey</I></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uxyloxandkendara.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Xylox And Kendara</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/7/02 2:12:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=74.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Kudos to the guides</span><hr size=1> The guides rule on this server.<br><br>That's all I'm gonna say.  I've petitioned 3 time on this server.<br><br>Response time on each Petition...<br><br>1)  5 minutes<br>2) 20 minutes<br>3) 15 seconds<br><br>All 3 times my problem was handled curtiously, effectively, and to my satisfaction.<br><br>Xylox <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uimogenelddar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ImogenElddar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 145<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/7/02 2:49:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=74.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Kudos to the guides</span><hr size=1> My Dwarf ran into a Dark Elf guide in The Nexus once and challenged her (or was challenged by her, I forget which) to a drinking contest.  It was great fun.  Ran into her in Qeynos some time later and had another drinking contest.<br><br>Something about seeing a guide role-play a drunk Teir'Dal just brings a smile to my face. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubjond.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bjond</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 387<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/7/02 8:13:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=74.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> I've petitioned a couple times ..</span><hr size=1> .. for minor things on FV that weren't time-critical and I think the quickest response has been about 90 minutes.  IIRC, &quot;stuck in terrain&quot; is the top priority for guides; it's easy to verify and easy for them to fix.<br><br>BTW, I've never had a bad experience with any guide on any server.  The only issue I ever had was with one GM that was refusing to obey a Verant directive to GMs -- this was Dragolen, if any of you happen to know him.  All conversations with GMs/Guides, even Dragolen, were cordial, though they can be a bit difficult to track down if your issue isn't urgent. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ublakkon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>blakkon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 105<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/11/02 6:05:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=74.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I've petitioned a couple times ..</span><hr size=1> I had to petition a death once, that once was responded to before I could even memorize all my spells.  Note... this was the middle of the day on a weekday.  I petitioned more out of reflex than any real belief that a) any guides were on or  b) that I woudl actually get a res out of it.  Pleasant suprise.<br><br>A merchant was out of place and not responsive  I petitioned this one, and it took about 30 min to respond, after which they immediately assasinate d the unruly cur.<br><br>I will say I have not had negative gm experiences ever, except the no answer type.  But our guides and gm's are the most courteous and helpful I have met.<br><br> <p>Lorec <br>Wandering Judge of the Tribunal <br>Excellent Tailor <br>Master Baker <br>Lousy Smith <br>Master Brewer <br>Master  Drunk <br>Aspiring Polyglot <br>Wannabe Alchemist <br></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm40.showPrevMessage?topicID=74.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm40.showNextMessage?topicID=74.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=74.topic&index=4><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm40.threadControl?topicID=74.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm40.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=74.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ff